DOMAIN,smtp.office365.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,outlook.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,hotmail.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,live.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,msn.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,office365.com

